item.title: Arunachal Pradesh Government suspended two officials over fire in daily market
item.description: Arunachal Pradesh Government suspended two officials over fire in daily market The Arunachal Pradesh Government has suspended two officials for alleged dereliction of duty during a fire incident that ravaged 700 shops in a market near here

item.title: Around 700 shops gutted as fire ravages Arunachal Pradesh's oldest market
item.description: Around 700 shops gutted as fire ravages Arunachal Pradesh’s oldest market Around 700 shops were reduced to ashes in a massive fire that broke out at Naharlagun Daily Market near Itanagar on Tuesday morning
